570
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:09,370
How audacious! Do you know who you are speaking to?!

571
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:15,330
Actually, I've only met you once.

572
00:40:15,330 --> 00:40:17,900
Why do you trust me?

573
00:40:18,780 --> 00:40:23,980
Even though I've never seen your face, I've heard your voice.

574
00:40:23,980 --> 00:40:29,960
I know that you are different from those that use music as an excuse for their ulterior motives.

575
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:33,140
Your voice puts me at ease.

576
00:40:33,140 --> 00:40:38,900
I imagined you as a cultured and fine gentleman.

577
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:42,770
So, my heart has developed some hope.

578
00:40:44,140 --> 00:40:46,480
But it turns out, I thought too much

579
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:50,810
I shouldn't have had the delusion of having you as a bosom friend.

580
00:40:50,810 --> 00:40:53,040
I am your bosom friend?

581
00:40:54,340 --> 00:40:58,740
Honestly, I have been a little impolite.

582
00:40:58,740 --> 00:41:02,290
All right, I will take the penalty of three cups of wine.

583
00:41:02,290 --> 00:41:04,840
- My Lord!
- You may leave.

584
00:41:10,780 --> 00:41:14,570
Earlier, I did not act properly. I spoiled your experience.

585
00:41:14,570 --> 00:41:16,580
I should take the penalty, too.

586
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:28,520
So, you think of me as your bosom friend?

